data.description: Stunning, like-new, and turnkey--all that's missing is your personal touch! Only 2 years old, this smartly designed home features an open-concept floorplan, large windows, fresh paint, and gorgeous wood laminate flooring throughout the main level, providing effortless day-to-day maintenance. Whip up delicious meals with joy in the pristine kitchen boasting granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, a beautiful backsplash, and an over-sized island/breakfast bar.  Spacious loft at the top of the stairs is perfect for a home office, media room, or bonus room of your choice! Positioned on a large corner lot with a private fenced-in backyard, you will have plenty of space to relax, play, and entertain. Never fall short on storage space with the nicely updated garage, featuring fresh paint, epoxy floors, and built-in wooden shelving. Don't miss out on your dream home and schedule your showing today!
